This is Debian prepackaged version of masqmail, a small mail
transport agent for hosts without a permanent internet connection.

This package is maintained by markus schnalke <meillo@marmaro.de>.
Its source can be obtained from

    http://marmaro.de/prog/masqmail

Upstream authors: Oliver Kurth, Markus Schnalke


